{"tid":835201,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"我影嘅相 你幾時滿意過？","createTime":"2018-09-24T16:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T08:53:49.000Z","uid":80658,"like":2,"dislike":96,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"75f41fb668fe9b44a38fd8622afa609272414e63","tid":835201,"uid":80658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"以前拍拖每次女朋友叫我揸電話幫佢影相都好大壓力，基本上無一次影完係滿意，到底係因為女人難服侍，定我真係手殘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我相信好多巴打絲打都面對同樣問題，點解我女朋友咁多要求？點解我男朋友影張相都咁揸ga？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢家NGO推出咗個情侶手機攝影班比大家玩下學下<br />\n覺得彼此間無乜溝通而又周不時因為影相而嘈交都可以報名，完全免費，有導師有小禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時間<br />\n27/9（四） 19:00-21:00 &amp; <br />\n29/9（六） 12:00-14:00<br />\n有興趣而情侶（24歲或以下）兩節都出席到既可以留tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢一兩日會覆返巴絲打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sorry希望攝影台巴絲有興趣啦"},{"pid":"c87ea83d1e29a2a4161b4a439d427e5bc6675704","tid":835201,"uid":104387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"廣告黎架"},{"pid":"7ce055503671409dd036ad4fdd31654f37bac677","tid":835201,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"想送帽?"},{"pid":"f3542e0bfa028d6855abe5af686a237e6191d4e7","tid":835201,"uid":163554,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T01:36:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9c58cd2d35dbfbfb986f6e17beaf30d6a9368bd","tid":835201,"uid":33939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T01:45:39.000Z","msg":"我條女豬西咁樣點影得靚？"},{"pid":"2da1835b0d25abf4cbfeff91bdfe6b621d25a1a3","tid":835201,"uid":108201,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"r